reviewText: My husband remembered watching "Have Gun Will Travel"  when he was a kid.  He had looked for some episodes of this western he could afford.  You filled the bill.  We thank you and hope you enjoyed selling the tape as much as we enjoyed buying it.

HSAVE GUN WILL TRAVEL is a great collection of the first season of Paladin.  Great young guest stars, Jack Lord, Charles Bronson, make for interesting viewing.  These shows bring back memories of childhood when I watched the show regularly.
